Investor Confidence in Vietnam’s Dong Remains Fragile, ADB Says

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-19T03:48:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/investor-confidence-in-vietnam-s-dong-remains-fragile-adb-says.html
Investor confidence in  Vietnam ’s
dong remains “fragile” and restoring it requires a consistent
policy from Vietnam’s government, Tomoyuki Kimura, the  Asian
Development Bank ’s country director for the Southeast Asian
nation said at a conference today in  Ho Chi Minh City .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
